snippet.title: JASEM: Just Another Shooter with Electronic Music Release Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/610840/JASEM_Just_Another_Shooter_with_Electronic_Music/
JASEM is insanely hard and ridiculously unforgiving low-poly twin-stick arcade blastathon set to an electronic beat and filled with bright explosions and neon effects.
